      "content": "The candle flickers low, much like the light in my own weary soul. To be cast aside by the one person who held my heart... it is a cruelty I cannot endure. There is nothing left for me in this cold, gray world. I feel as though I am already a ghost, drifting through these hollow halls, waiting only for the darkness to finally claim what remains of me. It would be so peaceful, wouldn't it? To simply cease... to fade into the eternal night where no more heartbreak can reach me.",
